  ('lifesciences.medical-devices', 'intro.p3', $q$Beyond regulatory submissions, accurate device translation protects patients and reduces post-market risk. Mistranslated instructions for use, software interfaces, or warning labels can trigger field safety corrective actions, customs holds, and Notified Body queries. We build a device-specific terminology base, apply translation memory across your product family, and route every file through independent revision so your IFUs, labeling, and technical documentation stay consistent from first submission through every label update.$q$),
